headline: Design Software Q4 Earnings: Autodesk (NASDAQ:ADSK) is the Best in the Biz
summary: As the Q4 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the design software industry, including Autodesk (NASDAQ:ADSK) and its peers.
